snippet.title: Why Amber Heard Should Be FIRED from Aquaman 2 RIGHT NOW
snippet.description:
Actors Johnny Depp and Amber Heard went through a public divorce and have since thrown allegations of abuse towards one another for years. Due to the abuse claims, Depp recently was asked to step down from the untitled third "Fantastic Beasts," film, but Heard has not been asked to step down from her role in the upcoming "Aquaman," sequel by Warner Bros. yet. Is this a drastic double standard and an example of the ME TOO movement gone wrong? Let's discuss...
